Einbettung dieser Praktiken in Diagrammkulturen und "Coding Cultures". Die Vielfalt der Diagramme wird auf fünf diagrammatische Grundfiguren zurückgeführt, deren spezifischen Funktionen und Effekte analysiert werden. Semiotisch und wissenschaftstheoretisch unterfüttert wird sodann eine Methodologie der Visuellen Linguistik entwickelt.  aGraphics and diagrams are important in linguistics: they visualise analytical findings, illustrate theoretical concepts and make it possible to analyse data in the first place. But how do they influence the generation of insights? What impact do they have on linguistic data? This book examines diagrammatical practices in linguistics and develops a methodology of visual linguistics.  aIssued also in print.  afunded by Schweizerischer Nationalfonds (SNF)  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Feb 2023) 4aDiagrammatik. 4aLinguistik. 4aSemiotik. 4aWissenschaftstheorie.  aLinguistics.  adiagrammatology.  asemiotics.  atheory of knowledge.2 aSchweizerischer Nationalfonds (SNF)efunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2020z9783110704563oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831106988480 cprintz978311069869540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110698732zOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110698732zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110698732/original  a978-3-11-069627-1 DG Plus DeG Package